						<summary>

						<p>On a pillar set up in the Śiva temple in the village.</p>						

						<p>VIRŌDHIKṚIT.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in the cyclic year Virōdhikṛit Vaiśs6kha, śu. 5 Sunday.</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of <hi rend="italic">bhōgamaṇḍapa</hi> for the god Sanita Mallaya and grand of land by the <hi rend="italic">mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Kammarāju Rāmayaīṅgāru for the merit of Dēvarāya Mahārāya and Hannayamma and Siddhayamma.</p>						

